'''«Vägimez'»''' ({{lang-hi|हीरो}} ''Hiro'', {{lang-en|Hero}}) om vn 1983 [[Indii|indine]] torafil'm. Ezmäine ozutez Indijas oli vn 1983 talv'kun 16. päiväl. Džeki Šroff edesti ezmäšt pärolid<ref>[http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-interview-with-jackie-shroff/20120519.htm Jackie Shroff: I am the original serial kisser (Džeki Šroff: Olen originaline serijne čoksuižiden tegii) / ''19.05.2012. Rediff.com''.] {{ref-en}}</ref>, sen fil'man tagut tegihe tutabaks. Minakši Sešadri-ki, enzne «Miss Indii 1981», fil'mzihe neciš fil'mas.

